name: Captain Tarpals
Lore: 'Gungan leader of the forces that patrol and protect the city of Otoh Gunga. Consistantly placed in the top ten of the Big Nasty Free-For-All.',
Text: 'Adds 1 to power of your other Gungans at same site. Opponent''s characters may not move to underwater sites. Once per turn, if you just drew a Gungan for battle destiny, may deploy that Gungan for free to cancel that destiny and re-draw.',
